00:11:14.630 --> 00:11:18.110
If this app had text, maybe we
would even want to do some

00:11:18.110 --> 00:11:21.460
synthetic text in terms of
maybe the game state.

00:11:21.460 --> 00:11:24.070
Is the puzzle solved
or is not solved?

00:11:24.070 --> 00:11:26.580
We could even index the move
list, all the rotations.

00:11:26.580 --> 00:11:27.830
Something that would
